  ],
  "remarks": "Arzamas Instrument-Building Plant is a Russian military industry company. Its manufactures parts used in Russian aircraft and unmanned aerial vehicles. It supplies weapons to the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation under Russia’s State defence order. Its management and employees publicly supported Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine, and sent material aid to Russian soldiers who participated in the war.",
